/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.620942762629873e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2687, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991880271579907, \"rank\": 0.0008038886131265903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stabbing occurred Monday outside the Gare de l'Est train station in eastern Paris.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2804, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.620942762629873e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city has been under a high security alert before the start of the Summer Games on July 26.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The soldier was hospitalized with a shoulder blade injury, but was not in life-threatening condition, officials said after the attack.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A statement from the Paris Public Prosecutor's office Tuesday identified the attacker as 40-year-old Christian Ingondo, who was born in Congo.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3063, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.620942762629873e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3069, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999996181018834, \"rank\": 3.8189841302793505e-07, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}, {\"begin\": 3143, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.8467231563621133, \"rank\": 0.17928553734845004, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgian_Congo\", \"score\": 0.6845085391703593, \"rank\": 0.4562629712523035, \"text\": \"Congo\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgian_Congo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgian_Congo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingondo was released from custody Tuesday morning and transferred to a psychiatric hospital that is under police supervision, the statement said.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Investigations into attempted murder and the suspect's background are ongoing, the statement said.\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, Ingondo was under judicial investigation on murder charges, the prosecutor's statement said.\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years later, in 2020, the investigating judges dropped charges against him and ordered a mandatory hospitalization.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of troops serve in the Sentinelle force for France's domestic security, created to guard prominent French sites after a string of deadly Islamic State extremist attacks in 2015.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3709, \"end\": 3715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9987187394167825, \"rank\": 0.0011345008991188697, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], 